OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1776066987
OL,3,CArtificial intelligence cameras
OL,4,Cdeployed to catch bad drivers
OL,6,FNew cameras, powered by artificial
OL,7,Fintelligence, are being used to help
OL,8,Fpolice spot bad driving in Sussex.
OL,10,FSussex Police will deploy the
OL,11,Ftechnology today (Monday 13 April),
OL,12,Fwhich is designed specifically to
OL,13,Fdetect drivers using a mobile phone or
OL,14,Fnot wearing a seatbelt.
OL,16,FThe force has not said where the
OL,17,Fcameras will be deployed, but believes
OL,18,Fthey will help tackle so-called 'fatal
OL,19,Ffive' offences.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
