OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1776066987
OL,3,CArtificial intelligence cameras
OL,4,Cdeployed to catch bad drivers
OL,6,FDuring the last three years in Sussex,
OL,7,F82 people have been involved in a
OL,8,Fcollision where someone was driving
OL,9,Fwhilst using a mobile phone, and 214
OL,10,Fpeople have been injured in a
OL,11,Fcollision due to not wearing a
OL,12,Fseatbelt.
OL,14,FThe use of the cameras follows a
OL,15,Fsuccessful trial by National Highways
OL,16,Ftwo years ago, which saw 458 offences
OL,17,Fdetected across seven days in Sussex.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1776066987
OL,3,CArtificial intelligence cameras
OL,4,Cdeployed to catch bad drivers
OL,6,FOf these, 330 were for a driver not
OL,7,Fwearing a seatbelt, whilst 118 were
OL,8,Ffor a driver using a mobile phone and
OL,9,F10 were for both offences combined.
OL,11,FThe cameras have been paid for through
OL,12,FSussex Police's road safety recovery
OL,13,Fcosts, which include proceeds from
OL,14,Fspeed awareness courses, and supplied
OL,15,Fby Acusensus.
OL,17,FThey will remain in place for several
OL,18,Fweeks, before officers will review how
OL,19,Fthey have worked, and if they are
OL,20,Fmaking a difference on the regions
OL,21,Froads.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
