OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1776066987
OL,3,CArtificial intelligence cameras
OL,4,Cdeployed to catch bad drivers
OL,6,FSussex Police says the use of the AI
OL,7,Fcameras comes at the same time as a
OL,8,Fnational roads policing, called
OL,9,FOperation Spotlight.
OL,11,FIt runs throughout April, and has a
OL,12,Fparticular focus on seatbelt
OL,13,Fcompliance.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1776066987
OL,3,CArtificial intelligence cameras
OL,4,Cdeployed to catch bad drivers
OL,6,FSussex Police Chief Constable Jo
OL,7,FShiner, who is also the roads policing
OL,8,Flead for the National Police Chiefs'
OL,9,FCouncil, said: "We regularly hear from
OL,10,Four communities across Sussex that
OL,11,Fthey are tired of seeing people using
OL,12,Ftheir mobile phones whilst driving,
OL,13,Ftherefore increasing the risk to
OL,14,Feveryone around them.
OL,16,F"While we endeavour to respond to
OL,17,Fthese concerns and proactively patrol
OL,18,Fwherever possible, the reality is we
OL,19,Fcannot be everywhere all of the time.
OL,26,@qD@POU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1776066987
OL,3,CArtificial intelligence cameras
OL,4,Cdeployed to catch bad drivers
OL,6,F"These AI cameras are not designed to
OL,7,Freplace modern day policing, but to
OL,8,Fenhance it. By embracing the
OL,9,Ftechnology available to us, we can
OL,10,Fbuild a better picture of driver
OL,11,Fbehaviour, influence behavioural
OL,12,Fchange and take action where necessary.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1776066987
OL,3,CArtificial intelligence cameras
OL,4,Cdeployed to catch bad drivers
OL,6,F"It is statistically proven that not
OL,7,Fwearing a seatbelt and driving whilst
OL,8,Fdistracted which includes using a
OL,9,Fmobile phone are among the five most
OL,10,Fcommon causes of fatal and serious
OL,11,Finjury collisions on our roads. We
OL,12,Fhope that this new initiative will
OL,13,Fhelp to reduce the number of these
OL,14,Fcollisions, which so often cause
OL,15,Fabsolute devastation to victims and
OL,16,Ftheir loved ones."
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@RO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1776066987
OL,3,CArtificial intelligence cameras
OL,4,Cdeployed to catch bad drivers
OL,6,FMark Baker, Sussex Police Road Safety
OL,7,FTeam Manager, said: "Road Safety is
OL,8,Feveryone's responsibility, and I
OL,9,Fwelcome the use of this technology to
OL,10,Fhelp keep people safer. If you know
OL,11,Fanyone who uses their phone whilst
OL,12,Fdriving, or does not routinely put
OL,13,Ftheir seatbelt on, please encourage
OL,14,Fthem to change their behaviour and
OL,15,Freduce the risk for everyone on the
OL,16,Froads of Sussex."
OL,26,@oD@UOUxD@QO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1776066987
OL,3,CArtificial intelligence cameras
OL,4,Cdeployed to catch bad drivers
OL,6,FPolice and Crime Commissioner Katy
OL,7,FBourne said: "One of my key manifesto
OL,8,Fpledges was to address road safety
OL,9,Fwhich is why I established the Fatal
OL,10,FFive Unit in Sussex - to tackle the
OL,11,Fmain causes of serious injury and
OL,12,Fdeath on our roads with a targeted
OL,13,Fdetermination. The trial of AI camera
OL,14,Fsystems is another promised delivered.
OL,26,@oD@NOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1776066987
OL,3,CArtificial intelligence cameras
OL,4,Cdeployed to catch bad drivers
OL,6,F"With 82 collisions involving drivers
OL,7,Fusing mobile phones and 214 people
OL,8,Finjured due to not wearing a seatbelt
OL,9,Fin just 12 months, I welcome the use
OL,10,Fof technology to enhance policing
OL,11,Fcapability and allow Sussex Police to
OL,12,Fdeploy resources more effectively.
OL,13,FThis technology will strengthen their
OL,14,Fability to detect dangerous
OL,15,Fbehaviours, intervene earlier and
OL,16,Freach more locations across our county.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1776066987
OL,3,CArtificial intelligence cameras
OL,4,Cdeployed to catch bad drivers
OL,6,F"But we all have a role to play. We
OL,7,Fmust not be afraid to challenge
OL,8,Ffriends, family members or anyone
OL,9,Fgetting behind the wheel if they are
OL,10,Fusing a mobile phone or failing to
OL,11,Fwear a seatbelt. Poor decisions put
OL,12,Flives at risk and no message or moment
OL,13,Fof convenience is worth the
OL,14,Fdevastation caused by a fatal
OL,15,Fcollision.
OL,17,F"I look forward to discussing the
OL,18,Fimpact and results of the AI cameras
OL,19,Fwith the Chief Constable in due
OL,20,Fcourse."
OL,26,@nD@AOUyD@AOU|D@HO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/12
